Wordpress Titan is a powerfull platform for developers to create fast OOP Wordpress themes and services while still following the industry standard of MVC. It bridges the devide between Wordpress coding style and provides more advanced methods for developers that will enhance the websites performance and over all speed by way of Helpers, Models, and Modules. Wordpress Titan is the most powerfull and light weight development framework for Wordpress on the market. Enjoy!

To install clone project into your wp-plugin folder and activate plugin, then get coding using Models, Views, and Modules.

I have included a few helpers and models to get you started.
